title: Defiance Line
summary: The Defiance Line was built for speed and agility. These light ships will get you around quickly, and will fly circles around opponents. Be careful, though, because one good hit could take you down.
full_text:
Defiance Line
The Defiance Line was built for speed and agility. These light ships will get you around quickly, and will fly circles around opponents. Be careful, though, because one good hit could take you down.
